text: Mullah Rezaul Islam is a Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Naogaon-6. ==Career== Islam was elected to parliament from Naogaon-6 in 1988. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:Living people Category:4th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:People from Naogaon District
title: Mullah Rezaul Islam
